Cell["\<\
Identifying every summand is just as fast, and reports each prime factor with \
its multiplicity, distinguishing mirror trefoils along the way:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"076c4708-20e6-4953-bf5c-ad9720b51826"],

